    <m:mn>5</m:mn>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>




</para>
<para id="element-96"><term>Solution : </term> 

Differentiating with respect x, we have :
 
</para>
<para id="element-97">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:mi>f</m:mi>
    <m:mo>′</m:mo>
    <m:mfenced>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      </m:mrow>
    </m:mfenced>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mn>5</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>4</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
    <m:mn>20</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>3</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>+</m:mo>
    <m:mn>15</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>



</para>
<para id="element-98">
Equating to zero, we have :

</para>
<para id="element-99">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mn>5</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>4</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
    <m:mn>20</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>3</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>+</m:mo>
    <m:mn>15</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>4</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>3</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>+</m:mo>
    <m:mn>3</m:mn>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>

<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mfenced>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:msup>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mn>4</m:mn>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>3</m:mn>
      </m:mrow>
    </m:mfenced>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>

<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:msup>
      <m:mi>x</m:mi>
      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
    </m:msup>
    <m:mfenced>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mn>1</m:mn>
      </m:mrow>
    </m:mfenced>
    <m:mfenced>
      <m:mrow>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mn>3</m:mn>
      </m:mrow>
    </m:mfenced>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
  </m:mrow>
</m:math>

</para>
<para id="element-100">
The roots are 0, 1 and 3. Now, differentiating with respect to x again,

</para>

<para id="element-101">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
